{
  "id": "62930d3bdd60a80020c064ed",
  "title": "動詞で説明する",
  "created": 1653804354,
  "updated": 1661758529,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "62930d3bdd60a80020c064ed",
      "text": "動詞で説明する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653804354,
      "updated": 1653804357
    },
    {
      "id": "62930d70aff09e00002907e6",
      "text": "　[酒は飲むべし]([川喜田二郎]による例)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653804401,
      "updated": 1653804418
    },
    {
      "id": "62930d6caff09e00002907e5",
      "text": " 　[名詞形へのとらわれ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653804396,
      "updated": 1653804408
    },
    {
      "id": "62930d54aff09e00002907e4",
      "text": " 　　[名詞形より動詞形]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653804373,
      "updated": 1653804408
    },
    {
      "id": "62930d45aff09e00002907e2",
      "text": "　[/kidaaam-92022284/文は形容詞から腐る]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653804358,
      "updated": 1653804371
    },
    {
      "id": "62930d93aff09e00002907e7",
      "text": "　 > 文をリッチにするため、[形容詞]を加えたくなる気持ちはわかる。だが、やるほど逆効果になる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653804436,
      "updated": 1661756091
    },
    {
      "id": "630c6b20aff09e0000bdadf3",
      "text": "　 [文は形容詞から腐る]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1661758241,
      "updated": 1661758243
    },
    {
      "id": "62930d50aff09e00002907e3",
      "text": " [/kidaaam-92022284/最短距離で心を打てる方法を常に模索する]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653804369,
      "updated": 1653804451
    },
    {
      "id": "62930da4aff09e00002907e9",
      "text": "  >文章を書くときは、意識的に「形容詞や副詞」を減らし、[動詞]で説明するといい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653804452,
      "updated": 1661756097
    },
    {
      "id": "62930d96aff09e00002907e8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653804439,
      "updated": 1653804439
    },
    {
      "id": "630c6bcaaff09e0000e59571",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]文章を書くときに動詞を使うかどうかのような表現形式の話ではなく、それ以前の部分で「[具体的な行動に注目せよ]」ということなのではないかと思う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1661758410,
      "updated": 1661758479
    },
    {
      "id": "630c6c18aff09e0000e59573",
      "text": "　[具体的]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1661758489,
      "updated": 1661758510
    },
    {
      "id": "630c6bd1aff09e0000e59572",
      "text": "　[行動]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1661758417,
      "updated": 1661758515
    },
    {
      "id": "630c6c39aff09e0000e59575",
      "text": "　[眼差し]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1661758522,
      "updated": 1661758529
    },
